anking products and services include checking accounts savings accounts cards certificates of deposit and online services home loans and personal loans and brokerage services individual retirement accounts education savings and insurance the company’s business banking products and services include checking accounts financing savings accounts and cards and online services treasury management services in the areas of receivables payables fraud protection information management and liquidity management international finance global trade and foreign exchange trust and custody services comerica bank provides personal and business banking products and services its personal banking products and services include checking accounts savings accounts cards certificates of deposit and online services home loans and personal loans and brokerage services individual retirement accounts education savings and insurance the company’s business banking products and services include checking accounts financing savings accounts and cards and online services treasury management services in the areas of receivables payables fraud protection information management and liquidity management international finance global trade and foreign exchange trust and custody services institutional investments insurance and retirement plans and corporate financial services corporate investment banking and capital raising services and specialty services such as captive insurance correspondent banking mortgage warehouse lending nonprofit tafthartley and pac services it serves auto dealers government and municipalities energy entertainment environmental services healthcare and education and technology and life sciences industries comerica bank was formerly known as comerica bankdetroit and changed its name to comerica bank in may  the company was founded in  and is based in dallas texas with locations in arizona california florida michigan and other states in the united states comerica bank operates as a subs